      <p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial" size="2"><b>THE COMPANY</b></font></p>
      <p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial" size="2">R &amp; G Cooper
      Engineering, based in Suffolk, have continued to exceed even their own
      optimistic forecasts.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>Founded
      in 1986, the company now enjoys an enviable reputation of working to high
      engineering standards and a level of quality that is second to none.</font></p>
      <div align="center">
        <center>
        <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="494">
          <tr>
            <td><font face="Arial" size="2">Well known for designing,
              manufacturing, refurbishing and installing fabrications for a wide
              range of applications, both in the UK and overseas, we offer a
              truly personal and professional service.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;
              </span>With a portfolio of projects, including specialist services
              for the quarrying and road construction industries – in
              particular sand, gravel and asphalt manufacture, the company has
              expanded to complete a number of prestigious commissions.</font></td>
            <td width="168">
              <p align="center"><img border="0" src="company.jpg" width="158" height="107" /></p></td>
          </tr>
